  ¡§Chai3-hoe7 lah! Peng5-iu2!¡¨ Hou5-li5 kong2, ¡§au7-pai2 ai3 e7 ki3--tit, ¡§Chhian-ban7 m7-thang siong-sin3 loh8-lan7 e5 lang5.¡¨ 
  32. Chng-kha-lang5 Kap Choa5 
  Chit8-e5 chng-kha-lang5 e5 kiaN2 tah8-tioh8 chit8-boe2 choa5 e5 boe2-liu. Choa5 oat8-thau5 ka7 ka7--loh8--khi3. In hau7-seN chiu7 an2-ni si2--khi3. Cho3 lau7-pe7--e5 chit8-e7 liah8-kong5--khi2--lai5, theh8 i e5 pou2-thau5 khi3 jiok choa5, ka7 choa5 e5 boe2-liu tok-tiau7 chit8-chat. Chu7 hit-si5 khi2, choa5 khai-si2 khi3 ka7 chng-kha-lang5 chhi7 e5 cheng-seN, cho3-seng5 chng-kha-lang5 chin-toa7 e5 sng2-sit. 
  Chit-e5 chng-kha-lang5 siuN7-kong2 an2-ne m7-si7-se3, bo5 kap choa5 kong2-ho5 be7 iong7--tit. I chiu7 chun2-pi7 chit8-koa2-a2 chiah8--e5 kap phang-bit8, lai5 kau3 choa5 e5 chau5-khut, ka7 choa5 kong2, ¡§Lan2 lai5 ka7 oan-siu5 pang3 hou7 be7 ki3--tit, hou7-siong7 goan5-liong7. Li2 ka7 goa2 e5 cheng-seN, si7 ui7-tioh8 beh po3-siu5, in-ui7 goa2 ka7 li2 e5 boe3-liu tok-tng7. M7-ku2, li2 ka7 si2 goa2 e5 hau7-seN, goa2 po3-siu5 ma7 bo5 siaN2m7-tioh8! TaN, lan2 hou7-siong7 bo5 sio-khiam3-che3, si7 an2-choaN2 lan2 be7-tang3 cho3 peng5-iu2 leh?¡¨ 
  Choa5 kong2, ¡§Be7-tang3! Be7-tang3! Ka7 li2 e5 mih8-kiaN7 theh8--tng2--khi3. Lin2 hau7-seN hou7 goa2 ka7 si2 e5 tai7-chi3, li2 bo5 kho2-leng5 ka7 pang3 be7 ki3--tit, chiu7 chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 be7-tang3 pang3 be7 ki3-tit goa2 e5 boe2-liu hou7 li2 tok-tng7 kang7-khoan2.¡¨ 
  I2-keng cho7-seng5 e5 siong-hai7 e7-tang3 goan5-liong7; m7-ku2, bo5 kho2-leng5 pang3 be7 ki3--tit. 
  33. Chng-kha Niau2-chhi2 kap Tou-chhi7 Niau2-chhi2 
  U7 chit8-chiah tou-chhi7 niau2-chhi2 khi3 chhoe7 i toa3 ti7 chng-kha e5 chhin-chiaN5. Chng-kha niau2-chhi2 lau2-sit8 koh tiau5-tit8, i chin ai3 chit-e5 tou-chhi7 chhin-chiaN5, jiat8-cheng5 ka7 khoan2-thai7. I an3-nai7 tou-chhi7 niau2-chhi2 chiah8 bin2-tau7, lah8-bah, chhi3-suh kap siok8-phang2. 
  Chit-e5 tou-chhi7 niau2-chhi2 iong7 chiam phiN7-a2 ka7 chiah-e5 chng-kha chiah8-mih8 phiN7-phiN7 leh, kong2, ¡§Goa2 sit8-chai7 be7-tang3 liau2-kai2, li2 na2 e7-tang3 jim2-siu7 chiah-nih8 phaiN2-chiah8 e5 chiah8-mih8. M7-ku2, che si7 it-teng7--e5, ti7 chit-chiong2 chng-kha sou2-chai7, li2 be7-tang3 ng3-bang7 u7 sim2-mih8 khah-ho2 e5 mih8-kiaN7 thang chiah8.¡¨ 
  ¡§KiaN5lah! Kap goa2 cho3-tin7 lai5-khi3 tou-chhi7, goa2 beh hou7 li2 khoaN3 mai7 leh, an2-choaN2 chiah-si7 chiaN3-kang2 e5 seng-oah8. Li2 na7 ti7 tou-chhi7 toa3--chit8--le2--pai3 ah, li2 chiu7 e7 kam2-kak kong2, ki5-koai3, i2-cheng5 na2-e7 ti7 chng-kha toa3 e7 tiau5?¡¨ 
  ThiN beh am3 e5 si5, chit 2 chiah niau2-chhi2 chiu7 lai5 kau3 tou-chhi7. Tou-chhi7 niau2-chhi2 chin u7 le2-sou3, kong2, ¡§Keng-koe3 chiah-tng5 e5 lou7-tou5, li2 it-teng7 siuN7 beh chiah8 chit8-koa2 tiam2-sim lah.¡¨ Kong2 soah, chiu7 chhoa7 chng-kha niau2-chhi2 jip8-khi3 chit8-keng chin-toa7 keng e5 chau3-kha. Ti7 hia, in khoaN3-tioh8 chin-che7 chheN-chhau--e5, chiu7 toa7-chhui3 toa7-chhui3 khai-si2 chiah8 ke-nng7-ko, chhai3-ian3 kap ki5-tha e5 ho2-chiah8 mih8-a2. 
  Bo5 tiuN bo5 ti5, in thiaN-tioh8 ki5-koai3 e5 kio3-siaN, chng-kha niau2-chhi2 chin kin2-tiuN, mng7 kong2, ¡§He si7 sim2-mih8 siaN?¡¨ Tou-chhi7 niau2-chhi2 ka7 in3 kong2, ¡§He si7 chhu3-lai7 e5 kau2-a2 teh kio3 na7-tiaN7.¡¨ ¡§Sim2-mih8!?¡¨ Chng-kha niau2-chhi2 toa7-siaN hoah--chhut--lai5. ¡§Goa2 chiah bo5-ai3 ti7 chiah8 am3-tng2 e5 si5 thiaN-tioh8 chit-khoan2 im-gak8!¡¨ Chit-e5 si5-chun7, mng5 hiong5-hiong5 khui--khui, 2 chiah kau2-a2 chhiong--jip8--lai5. In chiu7 koaN2-kin2 soan louh. 
  Chng-kha niau2-chhi2 kong2, ¡§Goa2 beh lai5 tng2 lah!¡¨ Tou-chhi7 niau2-chhi2 kong2, ¡§Na2-e7 chiah-kin2 chiu7 beh chau2?¡¨ ¡§ Goa2 kam-goan7 tng2-khi3 chng-kha un2-sim-a2 chiah8 tau7-a2 kap lah8-bah, ma7 bo5 siuN7 beh tiam3 tou-chhi7 the5-sim tiau3-taN2 chiah8 ke-nng7-ko, lim bih-luh!¡¨ 
  34. Hou5-li5 kap Ou-a 
  U7 chit8-pai2, chit8-chiah hou5-li5 khoaN3-tioh8 chit8-chiah ou-a hioh-ti7 chhiu7-ki, chhui3 ka7 chit8-te3 chhi3-suh. I chiaN5 hoaN-hi3, siuN7 kong3, ¡¨Che ho2 chhin-chhiuN7 si7 ui7 goa2 chun2-pi7--e5.¡¨ 
  I kiaN5-kau3 chhiu7-a2 kha, hoah kong2, ¡¨Gau5-cha2, ou-a sio2-chia2. Li2 kin-a2-jit8 khoaN3--khi2--lai5 chin sui2. Li2 e5 mou si7 hiah-nih8-a2 ou-kim, bak8-chiu si7 hiah-nih8-a2 kng. Goa2 siuN7, li2 e5 siaN it-teng7 kap li2 e5 goa7-piau2 kang7-khoan2, pi2 ki5-tha e5 chiau2-a2 koh-khah ho2-thiaN. ChhiuN3 chit8-tiau5 koa hou7 goa2 thiaN khoaN3 mai7 leh, goa2 chiu7 e7-tit-thang kheng2-teng7 li2 chiu7-si7 chiau2-lui7 e5 koa-hio7.¡¨ 
  Hit-chiah ou-a chiu7 ka7 i e5 thau5 gia5 koan5-koan5, khai-si2 toa7-siaN a-a-kio3. M7-ku2, ti7 i khui-chhui3 hit tang-chun7, hit-te3 chhi3-suh soah lok8-loh8 thou5-kha, hou7 hou5-li5 ka7 khi3 louh. 
  Hou5-li5 kong2,¡¨ an2-ne chiu7 tioh8 lah, che chiu7-si goa2 beh tih8--e5. Ki3-jian5 li2 sang3 goa2 chit8-te3 chhi3-suh, goa2 ma7 sang3 li2 chit8-ku3 oe7. M7-thang siong-sin3 ou-peh8 ka7 li2 po, ou-peh8 ka7 li2 pa-kiat e5 lang5.¡¨ 
  35. Phoa3-peN7 e5 Sai 
  Chit8-chiah phoa3-peN7 kau3 teh-beh si2--khi3 e5 sai, to2 ti7 i ka-ki7 e5 tong7-khau2, kan-ta chhun chit8-sut-a2 khui3-si-a2. Hu7-kin7 e5 ia2-siu3 long2 lai5 ui5 ti7 i e5 sin-piN. Sai ju2 bo5 kui3-lat8, in chiu7 ju2 oa2-kin7--i. 
