  36. Li5-a2 Kap Chhit-tho5 kau2 
  U7 chit8-kang, chit8-e5 cho3-sit lang5 lai5 kau3 i chhi7 cheng-seN e5 liau5-a2, khoaN3 i e5 cheng-seN. Liau5-a2 lai7 u7 chit8-chiah i siong7 kah-i3 e5 li5-a2. Chit-chiah li5-a2 tak8-kang chiah8-pa2 eng5-eng5, chai3 chu2-lang5 si3-ke3 khi3 chhit-tho5. 
