  Chit-si5, chu2-lang5 e5 tng5-kang koaN2-kin2 giah8 kun3-a2 tui3 li5-a2 e5 sin-khu ka7 kong3--loh8--khi3, kong2, ¡§ Ou-peh8 lai5! Li2 teh kun2 sim2-mih8 sng2-chhio3!¡¨ 
  37. Lok8-a2 kap Phah-lah8 e5 Lang5 
  U7 chit8-pai2, lok8-a2 ti7 chui2-ti5-a2 piN teh lim-chui2. I khoaN3-tioh8 chui2--nih8 ka-ki7 e5 heng5-iaN2, o-lo2 kong2, ¡§Beh khi3 to2-ui7 chhoe7 chhiuN7 chit-khoan2 chiah-nih8 sui2 koh ko-siong2, chhin-chhiuN7 chit8-teng2 ong5-koan e5 lok8-kak leh? Goa2 hi-bang7 koh-u7 bi2-le7 e5 kha lai5 phoe3 goa2 e5 ong5-koan. Goa2 e5 kha siuN san2, siuN se3-khou, u7 chit8-tiam2-a2 kho2-sioh.¡¨ 
  Chit-e5 si5-chun7, Phah-lah8 e5 lang5 tu2-ho2 kau3-ui7. ¡§Siu2¡¨--chit8--e7, chit8-ki chiN3 tu2-ho2 sia7-kau3 Lok8-a2 e5 au7-piah. Lok8-a2 khi2-kha chiu7 chau2. 
