  38. Ia7-po5 
  Chiau2-lui7 kap Siu3-lui7 u7 chit8-tiuN5 chiok toa7 e5 chhiong-tut8 teh beh pok8-hoat. Nng7-peng5 e5 kun-tui7 teh chip8-hap8, chun2-pi7 beh sio-chian3 e5 si5, Ia7-po5 sam-sim liong2-i3 m7-chai beh ka-jip8 to2 chit8-peng5. 
