  ¡§Gong7 gin2-a2, goa2 kong2 hou7 li2 thiaN. He si7 Ong5--sian--seN e5 gu5-kang2. I ma7 bo5 chhiuN7 li2 kong2 e5 hiah-nih8 toa7, kan-ta pi2 goa2 khah toa7 sio2-khoa2-a2 na7-tiaN7. Chin kan2-tan, goa2 ma7 u7 hoat-tou7 pian3 hiah toa7 hou7 li2 khoaN3.¡¨ 
